{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id6210b350-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t25/s41a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"41a"},"text":"§ 41a.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Indian inspectors","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Indian inspectors shall on and after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1909-03-04"},"text":"March 4, 1909","children":[],"tail":" be termed inspectors, and shall be included in the classified service."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id6210b351-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1909-03-04/ch297/s1"},"text":"Mar. 4, 1909, ch. 297, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/35/888"},"text":"35 Stat. 888","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id6210b352-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"execDoc","id":"id6210b353-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Documents","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"transferOfFunctions","id":"id6210b354-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For transfer of functions of other officers, employees, and agencies of Department of the Interior, with certain exceptions, to Secretary of the Interior, with power to delegate, see Reorg. Plan No. 3 of 1950, §§ 1, 2, eff. ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1950-05-24"},"text":"May 24, 1950","children":[],"tail":", 15 F.R. 3174, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/1262"},"text":"64 Stat. 1262","children":[],"tail":", set out in the Appendix to Title 5, Government Organization and Employees."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
